title: Running back sleepers and busts
itunes:title: Running back sleepers and busts
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – kick off the first of three fantasy shows by previewing the most undervalued and overvalued running backs and tight ends this season. The guys also review the top storylines following the 1st week of the preseason including the Bills and Texans quarterback battles.
